🎮【BLACK COLOR】 Tired of the white original shell? Don't like garish poor-quality stickers? This vent black PS5 plates perfectly matched your controller, and definitely makes your PS5 look like a member of the PS2, PS3, and PS4 console family instead of an outlier;
🎮【HEAT DISSIPATION DESIGN】The specially customized PlayStation 5 vent plates have cooling vents on both sides, which can allow better air circulation and prevent the game console from overheating, which greatly improves the heat dissipation performance of the PS5 console and prolongs its service life. The PS5 vent cover plates are designed to provide you with a smoother gaming experience;
🎮【Design for PS5 console only】This PS5 LED strip light is specially designed for PlayStation 5 Console, the ring design makes it available to paste directly to the PS5 cooling fan frame, integrated with the console. Compatible with PS5 Digital and Disc Edition. 💥NOTE: PS5 lights and vents faceplate ONLY, have not including PS5 console in the package;
🎮【Music Sync Lighting】With a built-in sensitivity adjustable microphone, when you open the music mode of this PS5 LED kit, the PS5 light strip ring will produce corresponding changes according to your BGM, allowing you to be more immersive when playing games!
🎮【Best Gift】Makes your PS5 Console stand out and look unique if you want to up the cool level of your PS5. And this PS5 led light strip also is the best present for your friend, brother, son, daughter on birthday, Fathers Day,Independence Day, and new year.
